          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">â€¢</span><span>A/B tested hidden pricing vs transparent pricing tables</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-gray-500 mt-1">â€¢</span><span>Monitored mobile vs desktop booking behavior</span></li>
